claim: Queen Latifah has appeared in the horror film Taxi.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Latifah released her fifth album The Dana Owens Album in 2004 , and has since appeared in a number of films , such as Bringing Down the House  (  2003  )  , Taxi  (  2004  )  , Barbershop 2 : Back in Business  (  2005  )  , Beauty Shop  (  2005  )  , Last Holiday  (  2006  )  , Hairspray  (  2007  )  and Joyful Noise  (  2012  )  .
